##jenkins-pipelines-exercise

* set db password which could be anything.
* command to remove existing directory
* clone the link
* Add jenkins user
 sudo useradd -m -s /bin/bash jenkins
 sudo visudo
 jenkins     ALL=(ALL:ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL
* port 80 problem: 
  Open an SSH terminal on your Jenkins machine
	Enter sudo systemctl status nginx
	If NGINX is running, enter sudo systemctl stop nginx && sudo systemctl disable nginx
